data.description: Weissport single home featuring 3 bedrooms, finished heated attic that could be a 4th BR, Eat in Kitchen and dining room. additional living area that could be a playroom, 2nd iving room or whatever your needs may be. 1st floor laundry. On and off street parking in addition to the 2 car garage. Fenced yard. AND if that isnt enough, there is also an inlaw Suite above the garage. Inlaw suite has a new roof, new plumbing and new hot water heater, features 2 BR, LR, Kitchen, Laundry and full bath.
